languages.text: {n}Отдав приказ, Иокаста с затаенной улыбкой вслушивается в вокс, а затем довольно кивает.{/n} "Отсек успешно провентилирован. Корабль очищен от слабых духом".
{n}Having given the order, Sauerback listens in to the vox with a furtive smile, then nods contentedly.{/n} "The compartment has been vented. The vessel has been purged of the spineless wretches."

languages.text: {n}Tras dar la orden, Sauerback escucha el voco con una sonrisa furtiva, y después asiente satisfecha.{/n} «El compartimento ha sido vaciado. La nave ha sido purgada de esos cobardes repugnantes».

languages.text: {n}命令を下したザウアーバックは、不敵な笑みを浮かべてヴォクスに耳を傾け、満足そうにうなずいた。{/n} 「区画の空気洗浄が完了しました。この船に乗った、意気地のない哀れな者たちは浄化済みです」
languages.original_text: {n}Having given the order, Sauerback listens in to the vox with a furtive smile, then nods contentedly.{/n} "The compartment has been vented. The vessel has been purged of the spineless wretches."

languages.text: {n}苏尔贝克传达命令之后，仔细听着通讯器里传来的声音，脸上带着一丝笑意，之后满意地点了点头。{/n}“船舱已经被封死了，这艘船上的所有孬种都已经处理掉了。”
languages.original_text: {n}Having given the order, Sauerback listens in to the vox with a furtive smile, then nods contentedly.{/n} "The compartment has been vented. The vessel has been purged of the spineless wretches."

languages.text: {n}Nachdem Sauerback den Befehl erteilt hat, lauscht sie dem Vox mit einem verstohlenen Lächeln und nickt dann zufrieden.{/n} "Das Modul wurde in die Leere abgelassen. Das Schiff wurde von dem rückgratlosen Abschaum befreit."
languages.original_text: {n}Having given the order, Sauerback listens in to the vox with a furtive smile, then nods contentedly.{/n} "The compartment has been vented. The vessel has been purged of the spineless wretches."

languages.text: {n}Après avoir donné l'ordre, Jocasta écoute le vox, un sourire furtif aux lèvres, puis hoche la tête d'un air satisfait.{/n} « Le compartiment a été évacué. Le vaisseau a été purgé de ces misérables lâches. »

languages.text: {n}Sauerback, emri verdikten sonra voksu çok hafif bir gülümsemeyle dinliyor ve ardından tatmin olmuş bir edayla başını eğiyor.{/n} "Kompartıman boşluğa açıldı. Gemi, bu omurgasız pisliklerden arındırıldı."
